#~ msgid ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Sponsor Level` and :guilabel:`Sponsor Type` are purely to "
#~ "distinguish different distinctions of sponsors. For example, if a sponsor "
#~ "has been attached to a company for multiple years, they would be granted "
#~ "a higher level (e.g. *Gold* level), which provides them with immediate "
